    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/c867a1a8581cd9d9bc71146c57b51761.poster.avif?t=1769695902\" width=1170 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/c867a1a8581cd9d9bc71146c57b51761.webm?t=1769695902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/c867a1a8581cd9d9bc71146c57b51761.mp4?t=1769695902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>前传邀请您参与游戏本体的战役故事之前发生的事件。您是著名的冒险家邓肯·铁眉，意外地卷入了“大政治”漩涡之中。 您注定要成为萨姆雷尼亚独立战争的英雄。游戏包含两个故事任务，以及一个无尽模式专属的地图布局等待着您的挑战。就像在常规的即时战略游戏中一样，在《要战便战：共享软件》中，您需要发展经济并招募军队，以抵御压倒性的敌军力量。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/21f6d22e214ec51002dfb2ed227709a4.webp?t=1769695902\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/8de3b63d23f6830ce1324d45bd8246ce.poster.avif?t=1769695902\" width=1170 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/8de3b63d23f6830ce1324d45bd8246ce.webm?t=1769695902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/8de3b63d23f6830ce1324d45bd8246ce.mp4?t=1769695902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>建造防御工事，组建军队，体验前所未有的战争。超过两万五千名敌人将进攻您的城堡。每支箭矢、每块投石机抛出的巨石和每名被抛向空中的敌人都具有物理建模，以便让战场真实而连贯。请确保您的弓箭手占据高塔，并拥有良好的视野，否则您可能会发现自己精心制定的计划因本方的防御工事而尴尬受挫。规划杀伤区域和阵地纵深是至关重要。您还需要在战斗中积极调兵遣将，以充分发挥士兵的优势。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/2d67e59435c64cd26659ce410540b1ee.webp?t=1769695902\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/49bf48d5aa53c62c9bbc8f3f8b0c5e76.poster.avif?t=1769695902\" width=1170 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/49bf48d5aa53c62c9bbc8f3f8b0c5e76.webm?t=1769695902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/49bf48d5aa53c62c9bbc8f3f8b0c5e76.mp4?t=1769695902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>任何强大的军队都离不开经济的支持和供养。食物、木材、石头、铁和黄金构成了城市经济的基石，如果您希望能及时应对来袭的敌人，就需要仔细关注您的物资供应。收集资源，选择存储位置，仔细规划您的扩张和升级。敌人不会轻易放弃他们的土地，未受保护的民用扩张将成为敌方入侵的牺牲品。利用难忘的商业飞艇进行贸易，为处于困境中的士兵运送救命的食物补给，或用石头重建城墙。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/858fd21ea1e12bb9b34202338f911c52.webp?t=1769695902\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/59ae013d0105b0af5898002c135a0141.poster.avif?t=1769695902\" width=1170 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/59ae013d0105b0af5898002c135a0141.webm?t=1769695902\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3043710/extras/59ae013d0105b0af5898002c135a0141.mp4?t=1769695902\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>当然，坚固的城堡城墙可以保护您免受大多数普通威胁，但既然存在魔法，为什么只依靠武力呢？学习魔法并困住阵亡敌人的灵魂吧。游戏中的法术不多，但使用任何一种都可以改变战斗的进程。建造魔法方尖碑，收获灵魂水晶，并尝试发出反派般的笑声，因为灼热的魔法光束将撕裂您的敌人，并召唤黑暗骑士追击逃兵。别忘了，您还拥有冻结时间的能力——毕竟，暂停游戏本身就是一种随时可供您使用的“魔法”。</p>",
